{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/encrypt-web-config/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"43428352-f5e0-5181-a33a-f1a94c996453","html":"<h3 id=\"webconfig-암호화\"><a href=\"#webconfig-%EC%95%94%ED%98%B8%ED%99%94\" aria-label=\"webconfig 암호화 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Web.config 암호화</h3>\n<p>web.config 파일 안에 있는 password가 plain text로 저장되어 있어 이것을 암호화</p>\n<p>암호화 방법은 <a href=\"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms998283.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms998283.aspx</a> (한글 : <a href=\"https://msdn.microsoft.com/ko-kr/library/dtkwfdky(v=vs.100).aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://msdn.microsoft.com/ko-kr/library/dtkwfdky(v=vs.100).aspx</a>) 참고</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\">cd C:\\Windows\\Microsoft<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>NET\\Framework\\v2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>50727\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 암호화</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\\aspnet_regiis<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exe <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>pef <span class=\"token string\">\"노드이름\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"경로\"</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 실패했을 경우 키 접근 권한을 부여</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\\aspnet_regiis <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>pa <span class=\"token string\">\"NetFrameworkConfigurationKey\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"NT Authority\\Network Service\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 복호화</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\\aspnet_regiis<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exe <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>pdf <span class=\"token string\">\"노드이름\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"경로\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>.NET web project에서 복호화가 제대로 안 되는 경우가 있어서 키 접근 권한을 주고 그 다음 암호화 진행\n(접근 권한은 한번만 주면 됩니다)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># config 파일 백업</span>\n<span class=\"token variable\">$todayString</span> = <span class=\"token function\">Get-Date</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Format yyyyMMdd\n<span class=\"token function\">Copy-Item</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"경로\"</span>\\web<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>config <span class=\"token string\">\"경로\"</span>\\web<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>config<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token variable\">$todayString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bak\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 암호화</span>\ncd C:\\Windows\\Microsoft<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>NET\\Framework\\v2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>50727\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\\aspnet_regiis <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>pa <span class=\"token string\">\"NetFrameworkConfigurationKey\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"NT Authority\\Network Service\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\\aspnet_regiis<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exe <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>pef <span class=\"token string\">\"노드이름\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"경로\"</span></code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/encrypt-web-config/","tagSlugs":["/tag/iis/","/tag/config/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2016-10-17T00:00:00.000Z","description":"보안을 위해 서버의 web.config 암호화","tags":["IIS","Config"],"title":"Encrypt web config","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/encrypt-web-config/"}}}